Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yee-haw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's officially\Napple bucking day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all those apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripe and juicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect for bucking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attention!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Sweet\NApple Acres code red.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I need all hooves\Nand claws on deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I calm down\Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Vampire fruit bats\Nare attacking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet Apple Acres!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought the fruit\Nbats usually stayed put
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in the West Orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The fruit bats do,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but these aren't just your\Neveryday ordinary fruit bats.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're vampire\Nfruit bats.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be durned if they\Nthink they're gonna sink
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,their fangs into my\Nblue ribbon apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooooh! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This here's our\Nentry into the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Appaloosa State Fair's\NProduce Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how much TLC goes\Ninto gettin' an apple
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to grow like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, when you go\Nbig, you really go big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Them Vampire Bats\Nwant to shrivel it up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,like a raisin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh,I'm sure if we\Njust let them know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,how special that particular\Napple is to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me,\NMr. Vampire Bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just wondering if,\Nmaybe, you wouldn't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving that really\Nbig apple alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, "yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But it could\Nhave been a "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first Vampire\NFruit Bat I've ever met
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and well, it might\Ntake some time for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to really understand\Ntheir language.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the meantime, this\Npest and his vermin friends
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,are gonna go\Nafter my prized apple,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and while they're at it, every\Nother apple in the orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These Vampire Bats are\Nnothin' but a bunch of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's a bit harsh,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Those vampire bats will{\i0}\N{\i1}give you a fright ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Eating apples{\i0}\N{\i1}both day and night ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ They rest for a{\i0}\N{\i1}minute, maybe three ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Then they're eatin' every{\i0}\N{\i1}apple in your apple tree ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ They don't care about nada,{\i0}\N{\i1}not zilch no, nothin' ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ 'cept bringin' about an{\i0}\N{\i1}orchard's destruction. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Now just wait a minute{\i0}\N{\i1}there's another side to this. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And if I did not defend them{\i0}\N{\i1}then I would be remiss. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ These bats are{\i0}\N{\i1}mamas and papas, too. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ They care for their{\i0}\N{\i1}young just like we ponies do. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Oh give me a break.{\i0}\N{\i1}You're being too kind. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ These creatures{\i0}\N{\i1}have a one track mind. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ The orchard is not{\i0}\N{\i1}their restaurant. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ But do they ever think{\i0}\N{\i1}what others may want? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ No, they don't.{\i0}\N{\i1}And that is just a fact. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ These bats they simply{\i0}\N{\i1}don't know how to act. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ That's where I{\i0}\N{\i1}have to disagree. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ They're loyal{\i0}\N{\i1}to their family. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Spreading seeds{\i0}\N{\i1}both far and wide. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ You see one comin' you'd{\i0}\N{\i1}better run and hide. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ They're big and ugly{\i0}\N{\i1}and mean as sin. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Will ya look at the{\i0}\N{\i1}state my trees are in? ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ They help your trees{\i0}\N{\i1}they'll grow stronger faster. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ They've turned my life{\i0}\N{\i1}to a total disaster. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Well, I, for one,{\i0}\N{\i1}don't have a doubt. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ These vermin must be{\i0}\N{\i1}stamped right out. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I second that;{\i0}\N{\i1}they've got to go. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ These bats they've{\i0}\N{\i1}got to hit the road. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ It comes down to{\i0}\N{\i1}just one simple fact. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ They crossed the line{\i0}\N{\i1}it's time to fight them. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Stop the bats{\i0}\N{\i1}Stop the bats. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Make them go and{\i0}\N{\i1}not come back. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Stop the bats{\i0}\N{\i1}Stop the bats. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Make them go and{\i0}\N{\i1}not come back. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Stop the bats{\i0}\N{\i1}Stop the bats. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Make them go and{\i0}\N{\i1}not come back. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Yes, it comes down to{\i0}\N{\i1}just one simple fact. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ They crossed the line;{\i0}\N{\i1}it's time that we attack. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Fluttershy,\Nbut I believe Applejack
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,has made the\Nbetter argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,These vampire fruit bats\Nsound downright dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's get to\Nroundin' 'em up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so that they don't destroy\Nthe rest of my orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fruit bat round up!\NFruit bat round up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me, but what if\Ninstead of rounding them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we let them have part\Nof the orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your\Npest-lovin' mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're only here\Nbecause they're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we built a\Nsanctuary for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they could have their\Nown apples to enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, they\Ncould even help
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the rest of your orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Vampire bats don't eat\Nthe seeds of the apples
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and when they\Nspit them out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they grow into even more\Nproductive apple trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Fluttershy, that\Nsounds real nice and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but every second we spend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,buildin' this\Nso-called "sanctuary"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is a second they'll spend\Ndestroyin' orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know\Nwhat it was like
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the last time there\Nwas an infestation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but Granny Smith has told\Nme enough stories about it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that just the thought of\Nit gives me nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Granny says we lost a huge{\i0}\N{\i1}section of orchard that year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They had to ration{\i0}\N{\i1}out apples all winter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the cider?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There was still\Ncider, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No cider?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No cider!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to round up\Nthese monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and we need to do\Nit now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If Granny Smith wasn't\Nwith Apple Bloom and Big Mac
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,checkin' out our produce\Ncompetition in Appaloosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd be here tellin'\Nus to do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Fluttershy, but\NI think Applejack is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish there was another\Nway we could convince them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,not to eat them in\Nthe first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So there's good news{\i0}\N{\i1}and bad news.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The good news is that\NI've found a spell
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that can get the\Nvampire fruit bats
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop wanting to suck\Nthe juice from the apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But in order for\Nthe spell to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the bats' full\Nand complete attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, I need you to\Ndo your stare on the bats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've used the stare\Nplenty of times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's not\Nsomething I take lightly;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made a vow not to use it\Nexcept in dire circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This circumstance is\Nplenty dire to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of the cider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't somepony please\Nthink of the cider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I just don't like\Nthe idea of taking away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing that really\Nmakes the vampire fruit bats
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,vampire fruit bats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It just feels wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't do this,\Nthere won't be any apples
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,left for anypony\Nhere in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that\Nfeel wrong, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's it going\Nto be, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do your stare\Non the bats or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...OK, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you wouldn't side\Nwith those icky bats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ewwww!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not icky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,First round of\Ncider's on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold it right there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta round up these\Nbeasts with wings first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's a-wastin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good work, everypony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we got them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all we need is for\Nyou to do your stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you sure I\Nreally need...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I really, really, really\Nhate to do this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope you\Ncan forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you go, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop\Nstaring, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one way to\Nfind out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo-ee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My crop is saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yee-haw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be drinking\Ncider all winter long!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank\Nyou for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't have{\i0}\N{\i1}done it without you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention\Nit, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my\Npleasure, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all we gotta do is\Nsweep up these cores
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can start bucking\Nfresh tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple bucking day, take 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,YEEHAW!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to collect those\Njuicy sweet apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're durn tootin', the\Nspell didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're going to have to\Ntake more extreme measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear ya', Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everypony, let's\Ntrack down those Vampire Bats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think these bats\Nare the ones that sucked
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,my apples dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the vampire bats\Naren't eating your apples,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, you're\Nour animal expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you know of any other{\i0}\N{\i1}creature that might be{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}capable of this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's only\None way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to catch\Nwhoever it is in the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do you\Npropose we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A stake-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The witching hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should\Njust call this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about the\Nrest of you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Fluttershy, it'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, darling,\Nwe're all in this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony leaves this orchard\Nuntil we solve this mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Does everypony have\Ntheir pony signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now remember Pinkie Pie,\Nonly use the signal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,if you see something\Nsuspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Something suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha doin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now\Neverypony split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll each patrol our\Nown row of the orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever or whatever is\Ndestroying my apples
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,has got to be\Nhere somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad\Nfeeling about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a really bad\Nfeeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:14:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That apple, it looks\Nso juicy and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspicious! Hee hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pony signal time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, there's\Nobviously no need to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,about that shadowy\Nfigure overhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll just go see\Nhow Rainbow Dash is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, or\Nyou'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Have it your own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that, you,\Nyou, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You scarecrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yooo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not Flutter-shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Flutter-bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get\Nher down from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy sweetness,\Nplease come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And do stop being\Na vampire bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:15:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you cut the\Nbat act and come on down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should just let\Nher come down when she's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Flutterbat on the loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See, she's back\Non her...branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's just biding her time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for the\Nright moment to pounce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, bats\Ndon't eat ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even vampire bats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe vampire\Nponies eat other ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking\Nany chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I\Ndon't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this was\Nactually our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do you\Nfigure that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}OK, so this is me;{\i0}\N{\i1}these are the bats{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and this is Fluttershy{\i0}\N{\i1}doing her stare.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spell was supposed to go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}right onto the bats like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But somehow the spell{\i0}\N{\i1}must have backfired.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It took the vampire fruit bats'\Ndesire to be vampire fruit bats,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and transferred that{\i0}\N{\i1}desire into Fluttershy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! We'll reverse the\Nspell and make it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are\Nwe waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's save Fluttershy before\Nthat thing eats us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow that bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nwe lost her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Fluttershy,\Nwhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If she keeps this up, your whole\Ncrop will be gone in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the least\Nof my worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want my\Nfriend back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never get her back\Nunless we corner her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and catch her so I can\Nreverse the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There she goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the only way we're\Ngoing to catch her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is if we find a way to\Nlure her closer to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if we can\Nlure her to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,how are we going to get\Nher to stay still long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to do\Nyour reverse spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! If only we had\NFluttershy to do her stare
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Flutterbat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, let's get\Nour friend back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Action stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for having\Nthe winning apple
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Appaloosa\NState Fair, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned into\Na vampire pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to eat ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wasn't a vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yes," I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Or "Yes," I wasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't try\Nto eat ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, and I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, I'm real sorry I\Ndidn't take your suggestion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget; now\Nyou'll get seeds that will
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,grow into even bigger\Nand better apple trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean what\NI think it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. More cider, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}OK. Got the part{\i0}\N{\i1}about the spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fluttershy turning{\i0}\N{\i1}into a bat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Building the sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to put in there\Nthat I came to see that my
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,short-term solution was\Na little short-sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that you shouldn't let\Nanypony pressure you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,into doing something you\Ndon't think is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you have to tell\Neven your closest friends, "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now how 'bout{\i0}\N{\i1}we celebrate our{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,stronger-than-ever friendship\Nwith a nice, ripe juicy apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I vant to suck its juice!
